### Development Environment:
- **TypeScript** (v5.7.3)
- **Wrangler for Cloudflare** (v3.109.1)

### Data Management:
- **Dexie** (v4.0.11) for client-side storage
- **Drizzle Kit** (v0.30.4) for database migrations

